958
01:08:56,083 --> 01:08:59,792
<i>* I feel mistaken *</i>

959
01:09:00,417 --> 01:09:03,458
<i>* And I was faking *</i>

960
01:09:03,542 --> 01:09:05,958
<i>* But I need your hand *</i>

961
01:09:08,167 --> 01:09:11,833
<i>* To get me through this life *</i>

